us.

08:24.738 --> 08:26.172 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
THOMAS RID, King's College
London: Hi.

08:26.206 --> 08:27.307 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHAEL MCFAUL, Former U.S.
Ambassador to
Russia: Great to be here.

08:27.340 --> 08:29.609 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Thomas, I want
to start
with you.

08:29.642 --> 08:34.881 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
