us. We have
heard that this is the Russian
government.

08:34.914 --> 08:38.451 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
How do we know that this was
Russia? How do
we know that this is a
sophisticated act that

08:38.485 --> 08:39.753 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
might take a state actor?

08:39.786 --> 08:42.722 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
THOMAS RID: So, there are two
bits of the
evidence.

08:42.756 --> 08:48.928 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The first is, who hacked the
DNC? The second
is, who gave the e-mails to
WikiLeaks? On

08:48.962 --> 08:52.832 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the first stage, who hacked the
DNC, imagine
a burglary, and you find the
fingerprints

08:52.866 --> 09:00.507 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in a house, and then you find
the same in
another house, and you know who
breached in

09:00.540 --> 09:02.275 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
one house, but not the other.

09:02.308 --> 09:07.046 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That's a bit the situation that
we're having
here. So, we have I.P.
addresses. We have

09:07.080 --> 09:14.254 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
server infrastructure. We have
SSL certificates,
so quite strong evidence to say
that the DNC

09:14.287 --> 09:17.457 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
