that are associated
with Russia.

09:17.490 --> 09:20.960 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Well, Michael
McFaul, are
you convinced that it was
Russia? Is this

09:20.994 --> 09:22.796 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
the way that they operate?

09:22.829 --> 09:29.669 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL MCFAUL: Well, first,
more generally,
Russia has tremendous capability
in this domain.

09:29.702 --> 09:35.208 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I worked in the government for
five years.
I witnessed it. I saw it. And we
should all

09:35.241 --> 09:42.649 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
just say that first. Second, the
reports that
we have, just like Thomas just
said, are very

09:42.682 --> 09:47.921 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
suggestive that it was two
different Russian
entities. The organization, the
company that

09:47.954 --> 09:54.327 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
