days ago.

09:56.930 --> 10:02.635 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And now today, we have many
senior U.S. government
officials also confirming that
they have strong

10:02.669 --> 10:05.338 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
