Russian entities.

10:05.371 --> 10:11.478 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Mr. Rid, I
want to ask,
is this consistent with previous
hacks that

10:11.511 --> 10:13.613 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
