have orchestrated?

10:13.646 --> 10:18.952 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Does this fall within their
definition of
what is allowed within how they
carry out

10:18.985 --> 10:20.753 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
cyber-warfare?

10:20.787 --> 10:26.326 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
THOMAS RID: So, the Russian
government and
intelligence community have been
hacking and

10:26.359 --> 10:31.764 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
breaching adversary computer
networks for
a very long time, literally for
20 years this

