44:16.921 --> 44:25.263 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
During a lull, rescuing people
from the second
stranded dinghy, he tells me
what he knows.

44:25.296 --> 44:31.636 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
BERTRAND THIEBAULT, SOS
Mediterranee: So there
were only men who were alive.
They were shocked

44:31.669 --> 44:44.649 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
