in the middle
of the boat because of the fuel
inhalation.

44:44.682 --> 44:52.223 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we have seen the dead women,
and, between
the floor and them, about five
other ones

44:52.256 --> 44:54.091 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
dead.

44:54.125 --> 44:59.697 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: This is a new
experience
for Amani Tekle, a former
refugee from Eritrea.

44:59.730 --> 45:05.903 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMANI TEKLE: Today was one of
the worst -- I
mean, one of my worst days,
because since

45:05.937 --> 45:15.580 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
