operations this year,
I didn't saw any dead body.

45:15.613 --> 45:21.586 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: For about
half-an-hour, the
raft floats free like a ghost
ship, before

45:21.619 --> 45:26.791 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
