move forward.

46:43.167 --> 46:47.405 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Eric Felice
lost his wife,
Texi (ph), in the crush. It
happened when

46:47.438 --> 46:52.276 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
salvation appeared on the
horizon. But for
Texi and the other women, the
rescuers were

46:52.309 --> 46:54.078 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
