46:54.111 --> 46:56.414 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ERIC FELICE, Widower: As we are
coming for
the boats, literally, we see the
water through

46:56.447 --> 47:03.087 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
