this place.
That place is OK. It's OK. I
didn't know.

47:03.120 --> 47:16.934 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
At the time, we see the rescue,
I was happy.
I went to call my girl, my
woman. She's already

47:16.967 --> 47:19.336 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
dead. It's finished.

47:19.370 --> 47:24.175 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: What happened
to her?

47:24.208 --> 47:32.950 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ERIC FELICE: I don't know. I
don't know. I
don't know.

47:32.983 --> 47:38.656 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: In the small
clinic next
door to the sanctuary, Dr. Erna
Rijnierse

47:38.689 --> 47:42.059 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
